{"tid":945304,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得西童真係自我膨脹得好犀利","createTime":"2018-12-17T18:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T16:07:12.000Z","uid":71379,"like":888,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"aff706cb050bae0ed7b26c631201f8e51494f080","tid":945304,"uid":71379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T18:44:31.000Z","msg":"其實一百個FOLLOW佢嘅人九十九個都係睇佢對波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢成撚日覺得佢嗰幾廿K follwer係佢啲FANS或者係鐘意佢先FOLLOW<br />\n於是就成撚日出埋曬啲POST懶係同啲FOLLOWER互動 又問問題又LIVE又盛<br />\n又成撚日老娘前老娘後 最近仲開埋啲POST指導人生 好似有幾千人睇住佢頭學做人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n撚有人想知你啲嘢咩 想睇你對波啫 你講鹹濕嘢就有人想聽嘞 <br />\n仲好自豪好多人SAVE同FORWARD佢啲大波圖 真係唔知做乜撚 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> FOLLOW咪又係想睇西童對大波波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 西童係我人生指導師 我要跟佢學做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c68300af7f9520b2f4e4e667b971ac993821d53","tid":945304,"uid":42374,"like":223,"dislike":14,"score":209,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T18:48:21.000Z","msg":"who"},{"pid":"88151d80a6895a2c733e6bbc0a7563880d8f5897","tid":945304,"uid":93998,"like":450,"dislike":25,"score":425,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T18:50:36.000Z","msg":"咁又點<br />\n你睇唔睇佢對波?咪又係睇"},{"pid":"9f9935d12b0397468b493813a9c67212eedf58a1","tid":945304,"uid":71379,"like":176,"dislike":21,"score":155,"quote":{"pid":"88151d80a6895a2c733e6bbc0a7563880d8f5897","tid":945304,"uid":93998,"like":450,"dislike":25,"score":425,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T18:50:36.000Z","msg":"咁又點<br />\n你睇唔睇佢對波?咪又係睇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T18:59:12.000Z","msg":"關乜撚野事啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3045d0c34869cc7b26ed23e127962c4b96b056","